I got put on an 6-day prescription of Methylprednisolone steroid that cost about $7 from my local Walmart.
For the first few days I felt overly sweaty and had to turn my house into an icehouse just to feel comfortable.
1.5 weeks after starting the steroids I’m starting to feel better and am ready to ease myself back into running.
